1. GENERAL PROVISIONS

1.1. This License Agreement (hereinafter referred to as the "Agreement") governs the use of the Telegram Bot "FalseMafia" (hereinafter referred to as the "Bot") provided by Hkmori15 (hereinafter referred to as the "Developer").

1.2. By using the Bot, you (hereinafter referred to as the "User") confirm that you have carefully read the terms of this Agreement, understand them, and agree to comply with them without any objections. If you do not agree with the terms of this Agreement, you must cease using the Bot.

2. SCOPE OF THE AGREEMENT

2.1. The Developer grants the User a non-exclusive, non-transferable right to use the Bot to participate in the interactive game "Mafia", in which each participant is randomly assigned a specific role that must be played accordingly.

2.2. The Bot is intended for gameplay with other real participants via Telegram and is not a means for profit-making, except for the purchase of in-game currency.

3. IN-GAME CURRENCY AND PAYMENTS

3.1. The Bot features an in-game currency system that the User can obtain exclusively by purchasing it with real money through the built-in payment mechanisms.

3.2. All financial transactions are carried out through officially supported payment systems, and the Developer is not responsible for any malfunctions or errors related to the operation of third-party payment services.

3.3. The purchased in-game currency is not subject to exchange for real money, refund, or any other financial operations, except as provided by applicable law.

